{"tid":1553685,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂電視【全攻略】1.1","createTime":"2019-09-08T16:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:13:02.000Z","uid":111315,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4020daae6d1b10bd5c43823990ab8f7876265be1","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前言</span></span><br />\n先多謝 嘧渡吾悉 巴打既啟發，讓<span style=\"color: orange;\">LennonTV</span>發揚光大。<br />\n第一集傳送門：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1403190/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1403190/page/1</a><br />\n趁等緊《香港人權與民主法案》通過，介紹下連儂電視既其他配備同心得。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmVwWrU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmVwWrU.jpg&h=457fa438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">觀眾</span></span><br />\n通常得幾種：前線、和理非、遊客<br />\n出發前記得預備不同類型既片，例如：<br />\n前線：MV、打氣類<br />\n和理非：MV、教學類、歷史類<br />\n遊客：歷史類（英文或其他語言）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">電視電池</span></span><br />\n我用左呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRjqgst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRjqgst.jpg&h=7d629de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fof5gsu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFof5gsu.jpg&h=45b156af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一舊20000mAh，有普通插頭位，大約可以支持個電視開住3.5至4個鐘；假設你要去200萬人遊行，行10個鐘，咁買3舊就OK喇！"},{"pid":"677e98af9b52599ebd2dcef603f6c4fe4c41372f","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">電腦</span></span><br />\n我用左呢個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iRtm2Mz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiRtm2Mz.jpg&h=dca41c32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPjEPrx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPjEPrx.jpg&h=1a9daa21&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nRaspberry Pi 3 Model B+<br />\n有藍芽，可連無線喇叭；<br />\n可連WIFI，以其他裝置（電話）操控；<br />\n有HDMI，可連電腦螢幕；<br />\n價錢便宜（大約是3份之1個電腦螢幕的價錢）。<br />\n另外請買一張Micro SD卡，容量越大，載片越多。"},{"pid":"1652d3a2a6d4751f6914ff3281af0cce9db867c9","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">安裝播放器</span></span><br />\n如果你買了這部小電腦，你可以到以下網址下載播放器（免費的），<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.libreelec.tv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.libreelec.tv%2F&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BrYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=7531f1bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.libreelec.tv/</a><br />\n按照裡面的教學安裝<strong>KODI播放器</strong>到Raspberry Pi的Micro SD卡裡即可。<br />\n安裝之後開啟小電腦，開啟SSH選項，讓Raspberry Pi 可以給其他裝置登入和傳送影片。<br />\n按Settings &gt; 按LibreELEC &gt; 按Services &gt; 打開SSH選項<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kmeabPR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkmeabPR.png&h=33f18142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08f0df25d9da069f82af79e7e6e21dd8c57388e3","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傳送影片到Raspberry Pi</span></span><br />\n到Connections，連你家裡的WIFI；記錄WIFI給你的IP address。<br />\n在你家用的電腦（或手機）安裝FTP程式，例如FileZilla或WinSCP。<br />\n開啟程式後輸入Raspberry Pi 的 IP address 。然後將你預備好的影片放入Raspberry Pi的Micro SD卡裡。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">控制KODI播放器</span></span><br />\n方法1：你可以裝一個無線Mouse到Raspberry Pi，然後選擇你想播的影片。<br />\n方法2：安裝Yatse（Android）<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.leetzone.android.yatsewidgetfree\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dorg.leetzone.android.yatsewidgetfree&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BrYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=7fc08628\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=org.leetzone.android.yatsewidgetfree</a><br />\n在你的手機打開Hotspot，將你的Raspberry Pi 連到你的手機，記得再抄一抄新的IP address。<br />\n打開Yatse &gt; 新增一個Device &gt; 輸入Raspberry Pi 的 IP address<br />\n然後透過這個Yaste，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你就可以控制身後看不到的螢幕了！</span></span><br />\nYatse有好多Setting和按鈕給你玩，記得玩熟先好出街。"},{"pid":"df9ed2d52d8d68933b176e1192393ab1ea77f0a2","tid":1553685,"uid":253169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc7936af6ffd5311b7e08a82af172041699c5716","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Yatse custom command</span></span><br />\n打開Yatse並連結KODI後，你可以按右上button新增Custom command。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s45XFwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs45XFwH.png&h=ca04d037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Take screenshot</strong><br />\nCap一個Screen到Micro SD card，讓你清楚知道現在個Screen是怎樣，尤其是要知道在播影片時有沒有Menu或其他Panel彈了出來。<br />\n按[+] &gt; Add from Media Center &gt; Call built-in &gt; 在Built-in command 輸入 &quot;TakeScreenshot()&quot;<br />\n如果你要查看圖片，可以在Yatse裡打開Screenshot folder瀏覽，或你在Play Store再下載一個FTP程式作查看之用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Activate Screensaver</strong><br />\n進入螢幕保護模式（只限沒有影片播放時，好似係）<br />\n按[+] &gt; Add from Media Center &gt; Call built-in &gt; 在Built-in command 輸入 &quot;ActivateScreensaver()&quot;"},{"pid":"679685c484555763ea9257c2119cc1a5321da2d3","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">RaspController</span></span><br />\nRaspberry Pi 的Controller。可以查看Raspberry Pi 的狀況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=it.Ettore.raspcontroller\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dit.Ettore.raspcontroller&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BrYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=6a7f129e\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=it.Ettore.raspcontroller</a><br />\n<br />\nRaspController可以儲存一些Commands，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UKYpXC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UKYpXC.png&h=4d832fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>打開藍芽Controller</strong><br />\n/bin/bluetoothctl<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[藍芽Controller]查看藍芽裝置</strong><br />\nlist<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[藍芽Controller]查看一個的藍芽裝置</strong><br />\ninfo XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX<br />\n(請在list裡的Mac address代替以上的XX)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[藍芽Controller]連結一個的藍芽裝置</strong><br />\nconnect XX:XX:XX:XX:XX:XX<br />\n（如果你的藍芽喇叭中途hang了，你可以靠這個再連一次）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[藍芽Controller]不連結藍芽裝置</strong><br />\ndisconnect<br />\n<br />\n<strong>切斷HDMI</strong><br />\ntvservice -o"},{"pid":"f59f40963ad0e4f51a0214733ebb15753cb7b4ec","tid":1553685,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"電腦幾錢？"},{"pid":"44fc6f31818172fad10ea1b01b329b6c388cedc5","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">螢幕右上角有個黃色icon？</span></span><br />\n這代表你的主機很熱，你可以在config file裡把它hidden<br />\n- SSH入Raspberry Pi（可用RaspController去SSH，但最好在家用電腦搞，比較方便，Windows機裝putty即可SSH）<br />\n- mount -o remount,rw /flash<br />\n- nano /flash/config.txt<br />\n- 將Cursor去到最後加 &quot;avoid_warnings=1&quot;<br />\n- Ctrl + X 離開<br />\n- Save<br />\n- mount -o remount,ro /flash<br />\n- reboot<br />\nRef.<br />\n1. 容許修改config file<br />\n<a href=\"https://wiki.libreelec.tv/config.txt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.libreelec.tv%2Fconfig.txt&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BrYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=36fd4211\" target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.libreelec.tv/config.txt</a><br />\n2. Hidden Yellow Icon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.raspberrypi.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=82373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.raspberrypi.org%2Fforums%2Fviewtopic.php%3Ft%3D82373&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BrYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=cca25f25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.raspberrypi.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=82373</a>"},{"pid":"a38bbec4155320f1dc4416d1c23e4d1a0e7b1c43","tid":1553685,"uid":44088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299822b349aa5d50714633568201ff91f2c93409","tid":1553685,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b245b30c013c8da7e3c467329eb23c530166a78","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:32:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支架</span></span><br />\n我整得太土炮，唔敢影相比你地睇。<br />\n大約就係喺木材鋪買左塊6分厚木板，叫佢地幫你切到可以放入你既背囊（可以切埋4隻角，令塊板易D放入背囊同冇咁易界到）；喺深水埗買左個釘入天花板的螢幕支架，釘入木板度；最後裝上螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n這個部份希望有巴打絲提供更好的方法！讓我地可以更輕及更輕便帶連儂電視出街。"},{"pid":"bfd1b3dfc0d169c7395c9c45aadd5465f3a6af3e","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">體力問題</span></span><br />\n如果你覺得裝備太重，建議買一個腰包，裝其他待用電池和行裝，分擔膊頭需承受的重量，不然行10個鐘真係好累好傷膊！<br />\n記得帶D野食同野飲，雖然好多香港人喺路上都會派=D<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防水問題</span></span><br />\n買定兩件透明雨衣，一件包住自己，另一件包住個螢幕同你既背囊，另外帶卷透明膠紙痴住D邊位。<br />\n或者一早用包書膠包好個螢幕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">後記</span></span><br />\n連儂電視只係其中一種和理非抗爭，大家仲可以：<br />\n<br />\n可以祈禱；<br />\n可以簽哂九百幾份聯署；<br />\n可以每15分鐘report 啲fake news pages；<br />\n可以去機場做旅客；<br />\n可以學定自衛術練定短跑準備行前一步；<br />\n可以罷買；<br />\n可以唔幫襯中資；<br />\n可以唔幫襯盲挺港共既舖頭；<br />\n可以做翻譯；<br />\n可以去連儂隧道幫手黐poster；<br />\n可以去Twitter文宣；<br />\n可以將自己變成流動連儂牆；<br />\n可以教育你既下一代要分是非黑白；<br />\n可以將MPF啲大中華同香港基金轉走哂佢；<br />\n可以㩒哂啲錢出黎，買哂外幣；<br />\n可以取消哂啲中資戶口；<br />\n可以罷課；<br />\n可以為下次全港大罷工做定準備；<br />\n可以運用你既創意，為香港人既抗爭提供更有效既方法。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d45aeca31a8a842a0ace4ed27ce89b4f13c5e8bd","tid":1553685,"uid":115955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:32:54.000Z","msg":"（再開）全城唔知係咪最大既義教防身術班上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1553491</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef300ace2df9deb17dd8f4ed89c406863128b9d3","tid":1553685,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"8ff23da7d150a0d8718917ef0430a41f0cb6176a","tid":1553685,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"原來有D咁既野"},{"pid":"38479822784eda827593a71a7e8aa9172da34c92","tid":1553685,"uid":293921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:34:54.000Z","msg":"STRONG POST"},{"pid":"0168c1e06a5ecd5fb63950bb19e3e2c4f70910e3","tid":1553685,"uid":111315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f59f40963ad0e4f51a0214733ebb15753cb7b4ec","tid":1553685,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"電腦幾錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:34:58.000Z","msg":"不多於400HKD"},{"pid":"018d29e17cfde53ba6e4b10f9b8d42f514617bc1","tid":1553685,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"勁，幫推"},{"pid":"c3a4c3d22fab33c548c2274246b41870b8662060","tid":1553685,"uid":12419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"之前見到你 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ae1f3257fe0a499e0c31424605fd8b7830d969","tid":1553685,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"其實瘋狂loop濫暴畫面我覺得幾有用"},{"pid":"d4492cb8251d2b1c3eddbde452bb52286aaa665c","tid":1553685,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:40:20.000Z","msg":"好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af812bed3f76840073da02cae1a4243f3c1beb1","tid":1553685,"uid":89882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"巴打想問下ipad有冇攻略"},{"pid":"6e138e677ea6e9769713647265b5954562cacbc5","tid":1553685,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"有兩三個22~24寸mon 可sponsor<br />\n有意tg我 superon9999"},{"pid":"92dfa66b908f38854b7632b1f9c5b9ad191f6d27","tid":1553685,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"其實好撚弱智"}]}